You see this beautifully done in #emph[Fourth Wing], where Violet and Xaden have their most passionate moments happening while there's still action going on around them. They're fighting war games, assassins are trying to kill them, he's revealed his rebellion... but the threat from the outside world never ceases. Their romance develops #emph[as a result] of the pressure, not in spite of it, and each stolen moment holds the weight of the possibility that "this could be the last time."


