  example-rows: (
    ([Magic costs suddenly change in the love scene (Ch. 14)], ["In the scene where [character] uses magic in Ch. 14, did the cost feel consistent with how magic worked earlier? Did anything pull you out of the moment?"]),
  ),
  rows: (
    ([], []),
    ([], []),
    ([], []),
  ),
  row-height: 75pt,
  fill-strategy: "wider_rows",
)


#hint[Pay special attention to romantic scenes when writing your questions. These are the moments where readers are most emotionally engaged but also most likely to notice when rules bend. A beta reader who flags "I didn't believe they could be alone here" is catching a selective enforcement problem.]


